  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bae\u0bca\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1- \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An Army officer assaulted a person at a gas station - Two civilians arrested - Investigations begin",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Army Spokesperson has said that investigations have been started regarding the incident where a person was kicked by an Army officer at a fuel filling station.",
        "Army Spokesman Brigadier Nilantha Premaratna has stated that internal investigations have started regarding the kicking of a person at a fuel station by an army officer. He also mentioned that this incident took place when the police brought some Asians in front of the army for using obscenities.",
        "The army spokesman said that two people who behaved in a very violent manner have been handed over to the police.",
        "A video of an army officer kicking a commoner at a petrol station has surfaced on social media.",
        "The video shows the man being grabbed by the soldiers and dragged in front of the officer and kicked by him. A police officer then tries to bring the situation under control.",
        "One army officer can be seen calling another, arguing with him and warning the person found at the petrol station.",
        "There are comments in the media and social media that incidents of attacks by the military and police on civilians who have been waiting for days for fuel have increased due to the fuel crisis.",
        "It has been pointed out that these incidents are taking place even as the army and police are trying to get fuel despite the people who have been waiting for days to get even a small amount of fuel.",
        "An Army officer from Wegera Army Camp kicked a person who had been waiting for days to get fuel at the Yakapitiya filling station on Kurunagal Road in Tampulla when he questioned why they were giving fuel to the army instead of to the public."
      ],
